title: 820-3536 not turning on
820-3536 not turning on
message:
You forgot 3V3_S5, which is very important.
If pulses, then check SMC_PM_G2_EN.
Also check diode mode to ground on all big coils.

title: 820-3536 not turning on
message:
PM_RSMRST_L 0,275V o pulse when SMC_ONOFF is triggered
PM_PWRBTN_L starts high at 3.42V when triggering the SMC_ONOFF drops 0.355V

Do not enter SMC Bypass mode

title: 820-3536 not turning on
message:
3V3_SUS must appear first, in order to get high PM_RSMRST_L.

Are you sure PM_SLP_SUS_L is missing?
PM_BATLOW_L is still high?
Check PM_DSW_PWRGD, SMC_ADAPTER_EN and PCH_DSWRMEN.
